{"word":"H6148 - ערב - ‛ârab - aw-rab'","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: ערב"},{"paragraph":"Transliteration: ‛ârab"},{"paragraph":"Phonetic: aw-rab'"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இன்பமாயிரு, நேசி, பிணைப்படு, பிணைப்படுகிற, பிரியமாயிரு, உத்திரவாதியாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to pledge, to exchange, to mortgage, to engage, to occupy, to undertake for, to give pledges, to be (or to become) surety, to take on a pledge, to give in pledge"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to take on a pledge, to go surety for, to guarantee"},{"paragraph":"2) to give in pledge"},{"paragraph":"3) to exchange"},{"paragraph":"4) to pledge"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hithpael)"},{"paragraph":"1) to exchange pledges"},{"paragraph":"2) to have fellowship with, to share"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Cognate: <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H4627 - מערב - ma‛ărâb - mah-ar-awb'/4627\">H4627</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H6148 - ערב - ‛ârab - aw-rab'/6148\">H6148</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H6161 - ערבּה - ‛ărûbbâh - ar-oob-baw'/6161\">H6161</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H6162 - ערבון - ‛ărâbôn - ar-aw-bone'/6162\">H6162</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H8594 - תּערבה - ta‛ărûbâh - tah-ar-oo-baw'/8594\">H8594</a>"}]}